name: Feed me food
description:
In the process of finding food, you will encounter all kinds of difficulties, and one will die if you are not careful. You must use your intelligent mind to avoid all kinds of sudden dangers in order to live in this dangerous world. Start your journey of cannibals as soon as possible.

Game Features:
* Independent passes allow you to experience the fun of the game in fragmented time.
* All kinds of obstacles let you use your brains in your leisure time.
* A variety of interesting props, skin makes the game interface no longer monotonous.
